data.static-generation-with-data-#Static Gene:
For pages where content depends on external data, such as blog posts, the getStaticProps function is utilized to fetch and pre-render the necessary data during build time.
// Example MDX Blog Post Component
import React from 'react';
function BlogPost({ title, content }) {
  return (
    <article>
      <h1>{title}</h1>
      <div dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: content }} />
    </article>
  );
}
export default BlogPost;
